      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im struggling with a python script. i'm trying to process these massive csv files using pandas but i keep getting a MemoryError when i try to load the whole thing at once. i think i should use a generator instead of a list comprehension to save space but im not 100% sure how it actually impacts the ram. can u explain the difference in terms of memory footprint?",
